++ miscset v 1.1.0 ++ 2017/02/24

changed mgrepl to default log.fun=all and added na.replace option
fixed collapse.data.frame for sep=NULL and list objects in collapsed columns
do.rbind deprecated, suggested data.table::rbindlist
strextr deprecated, suggested stringr::str_extract and stringr::str_extract_all
strpart deprecated and replaced with str_part
strrev deprecated and replaced with str_rev
added src/init.c to fix R-devel r72246 note on R_registerRoutines/R_useDynamicSymbols

